MOVS TO WERN SOLE 986 WITH ANOTHER LOW PERHAPS CENTRED NEAR NERN IRELAND
998 BY MIDDAY. CURRENT INDICATIONS ARE FOR THE LOW TO DRIFT TO SHANNON 990
BY MONDAY AFTERNOON AND REMAIN SLOW-MOV THROUGH TUESDAY ALTHOUGH THERE IS
LOW CONFIDENCE FOR DETAIL. PRESSURE REMAINING HIGH ACROSS SCANDINAVIA AND
