MUCH OF THE PERIOD. THERE IS A RISK OF GALES AFFECTING FAR NWERN WATERS LATER
ON SUNDAY ESPECIALLY FAIR ISLE AND THIS RISK MAY EXTEND FURTHER E AND S
FOR A TIME ON MONDAY. WINDS PERHAPS DECR GENERALLY ON TUESDAY WITH LOW CONFIDENCE
